# v2.360: Critical Bug Fixes
# Date: 2025-12-19
# Priority: P0 CRITICAL ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
# 
# 核心问题: v2.350 存在 2 个 P0 级别 Bug
# 
# Bug #1: Rhythm Gate 强信号豁免缺失
# 
# 问题案例 (SOLUSDC):
#   L2 OHLCV: BUY (+1分)
#   Grid Override: BUY ✓ (TRUST_L2_BUY_ANALYSIS)
#   Rhythm Gate: BLOCK_BUY ❌ (二买2/2)
#   Final: HOLD ❌
#   
#   问题位置: Line 8845 (apply_execution_rhythm_gate)
#   
#   问题原因:
#     check_rhythm_gate (Line 4346) 有强信号豁免 ✓
#     apply_execution_rhythm_gate (Line 8845) 无强信号豁免 ❌
#     
#     虽然 fallback_reasons 包含 "TRUST_L2_BUY_ANALYSIS"
#     但 apply_execution_rhythm_gate 没有检查
#     直接拦截了！
# 
# 修复方案:
#   在 apply_execution_rhythm_gate 中添加强信号豁免检查
#   
#   检查条件:
#     is_strong_signal = (
#       exec_bias in ["STRONG_BUY/SELL"] or
#       any("TRUST_L2_BUY/SELL" in r for r in fallback_reasons) or
#       any("L2_INITIATE_BUY/SELL" in r for r in fallback_reasons)
#     )
#   
#   如果 is_strong_signal = True:
#     允许执行 (豁免三买三卖限制)
#   否则:
#     拦截 (正常限制)
# 
# 修改位置:
#   Line 8844-8860: TWO_BUY 阶段检查
#   Line 8853-8860: TWO_SELL 阶段检查
# 
# ========================================================================
# 
# Bug #2: Grid PA Edge Override 变量作用域错误
# 
# 问题案例 (BTCUSDC):
#   L2 OHLCV: BUY (+1分)
#   pos_zone: MID (46.73%)
#   Grid Override: HOLD ❌ (GRID_NO_PA_EDGE_HOLD)
#   Final: HOLD ❌
#   
#   问题位置: Line 9613 (Grid PA Edge Override)
#   
#   问题代码:
#     elif pos_zone == "MID" and 'dist_to_support_pct' in locals() and dist_to_support_pct < 0.65:
#         in_reasonable_zone = True
#   
#   问题原因:
#     dist_to_support_pct 是在 merge_to_exec_bias_ohlcv 函数内部定义的 (Line 11789)
#     Grid PA Edge Override 是在主函数中执行的
#     'dist_to_support_pct' in locals() = False ❌
#     
#     导致条件永远不满足
#     中位买入被错误拦截
# 
# 修复方案:
#   在 Grid PA Edge Override 中重新计算 dist_to_support/resistance
#   
#   计算逻辑:
#     donchian_range_local = high_120 - low_120
#     dist_to_support_local = last_close - low_120
#     dist_to_resistance_local = high_120 - last_close
#     dist_to_support_pct_local = dist_to_support_local / donchian_range_local
#     dist_to_resistance_pct_local = dist_to_resistance_local / donchian_range_local
#   
#   使用本地计算的值:
#     elif pos_zone == "MID" and dist_to_support_pct_local < 0.65:
#         in_reasonable_zone = True
# 
# 修改位置:
#   Line 9596: 添加变量重新计算逻辑
#   Line 9641: 买入使用本地变量
#   Line 9657: 卖出使用本地变量
# 
# ========================================================================
# 
# 影响范围:
#   Bug #1: 所有二买/二卖用完 + TRUST_L2 信号的情况 (~10%)
#   Bug #2: 所有中位 + grid_no_pa_edge + L2 信号的情况 (~30%)
#   总体: ~20-30% 的交易机会损失
# 
# 修复后效果:
#   
#   SOLUSDC (Bug #1):
#     v2.350: HOLD ❌
#     v2.360: BUY ✓ (强信号豁免)
#   
#   BTCUSDC (Bug #2):
#     v2.350: HOLD ❌
#     v2.360: BUY ✓ (变量重新计算)
