# ========================================================================
# v2.380: Critical Fix - Rhythm Gate Position Priority Bypass
# Date: 2025-12-19
# Priority: P0 CRITICAL ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
# 
# 核心问题: v2.370 Rhythm Gate 无视 Position Priority
# 
# 问题描述:
#   Rhythm Gate (apply_execution_rhythm_gate) 不检查 position_priority
#   导致极端位置无法绕过配额限制
# 
# 问题案例:
#   输入:
#     pos_ratio: 2% (EXTREME_LOW)
#     two_buy_used: 3/3
#     L2: BUY
#     final_action: BUY
#   
#   v2.370 执行:
#     ① Position Priority:
#        pos_ratio < 5% and action = BUY
#        → bypass_all_gates = True ✓
#     
#     ② Grid PA Gate:
#        检查 bypass_all_gates → BYPASSED ✓
#     
#     ③ UNCLEAR Gate:
#        检查 bypass_most_gates → BYPASSED ✓
#     
#     ④ Rhythm Gate:
#        ❌ 没有检查 bypass_all_gates!
#        two_buy_used >= 3 → BLOCK_BUY ❌
#     
#     ⑤ 最终: HOLD ❌
#   
#   预期: BUY ✓ (Position Priority 应该最高)
